description: Redevelopment of the site to provide 440 residential units (use class C3) and 2069sqm of flexible commercial / community floorspace (Use classes A1-A4 / B1/D1/D2) in five new buildings (A-E) ranging from 2 to 16 storeys in height with associated plant at roof level, together with associated car parking, open space, landscaping and public realm works.
